criminal, Chibuzor Henry, alias Vampire at the High Court premises in Owerri, Imo State, the state police command weekend raided the Owerri Prisons and recovered 264 mobile telephone sets from the prison inmates. January 31, 2017 In "News" BENIN—EDO State Police Commissioner, Mr Olayinka Balogun, yesterday, said the Command was still awaiting more details from the Prison authorities as regards the jail break at Oko Medium Prison, Benin City on Sunday. August 21, 2012 In "News"